<taxonomicNameLabel box="[663,725,1866,1892]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(anterior elytral band consisting of elongated spots). Certain identification possible on the basis of morphology of aedeagus with wide and long parameres.
</paragraph>
